                     <title>Maṣḥafa geṣṣawe</title>
                     
                     <note>Volume 3 of 3 arranged for the months of the year and major feasts: Sanē, fol. 1v-90v; Ḥamlē, fol. 90v-146r; Naḫasē, fol. 146r-177v; Pāgwmēn, fol. 177v-185v. See also <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML1165">Vol. 1 = EMML 1165</ref> and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML1166">Vol. 2 = EMML 1166</ref>
                        
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
